item.content:encoded:
Cartoon Hot Racer 3D is not only a racing simulation but also a car driving with 3D cartoon game art animation. Your mission is to choose the driving job you like and enjoy the huge open world. You have a chance to experience the realistic physics game engine while driving. Have a good time in Cartoon Hot Racer 3D!
WASD or arrow keys – drive, B – look back, Shift – use nitro, Space bar – use handbrake, Esc – pause

item.content:encoded:
Ice princess in the game is very personalized.Ice princess doesn’t like traditional and conservative long skirts, she likes fashionable shorts. Players can choose clothes with various patterns for ice princess, including beautiful girl soldiers, cats and dogs, stars and butterflies,and so on. In addition, players can also choose different hair styles for ice princess. Snow white hair can reflect the temperament of ice princess more, blue hair can experience the personality of ice princess more, no matter what color of hair, players can enjoy the beautiful game.

item.content:encoded:
The sexy red-haired female celebrity is going to the studio to shoot an advertisement today, but her makeup artist can not rush to the studio in time due to traffic jams. Now, it is time for you to do makeup and take pictures for the female celebrity. Make a complete makeover for the female celebrity at the spa, relax with her in the nail spa, help her choose the right clothes, and create the perfect makeup with cool makeup. The female star thank you very much for your help and give you a signed photo as a gift!
Click to play.

item.content:encoded:
Geisha Glass Skin Routine is a very traditional makeup game, in which you need to apply makeup to a Japanese geisha. Japanese entertainers who perform traditional Japanese artforms, such as traditional dance and singing. They are distinctively characterized by the kimono and the oshiroi makeup they wear. Finally, choose some good-looking accessories for the geisha, such as fans and headwear. Japanese Geisha is very beautiful, come and experience this game!
Click to play.

item.content:encoded:
Summer is here, and the hot weather is unbearable! There is no doubt that everyone hopes that they can spend the whole summer by the sea. Who would refuse white sand beaches and swimming in clear waters? For fashionistas, spending summer by the sea is a great time to wear cute wave dresses, tight shorts and floral tops! The princesses want to become qualified fashionistas, but they need your help. Come and choose suitable summer dresses for the princesses, and finally prepare some beautiful accessories!
Click to play.

item.content:encoded:
Taylor is a very well-behaved boy. Because the weather suddenly became very cold, Taylor had a fever. She couldn’t wear her favorite skirt. Her mother called the doctor. The doctor provided Taylor with some medicine and advice to make sure It can heal her within a few days. For Taylor, this is indeed a difficult time. She needs you now and you need to take care of Taylor until she recovers.
Mouse click or tap to play.

item.content:encoded:
Have you played the game Angry Birds? Neon Shot is this neon pixel style game. This is a fun physics catapult game. The game uses a very classic pixel style. Your task is to launch a ball to crash all targets. And try to collect all the coins. The ball follows the principles of physics, and its trajectory will change according to the law of reflection. Have you thought about how to launch it? If you like this game, don’t forget to share it with your friends!
Click and drag the mouse to play.

When selecting, you can also modify the character’s skin color. There are foxes, chickens, cows, and a new animal: a rhino. Notice! You only have one chance, if you are killed then you will fail! […]
item.content:encoded:
You need to avoid enemy shooting in different scenarios. Unlike other games, the Bullet Bonanza game is an animal character. When selecting, you can also modify the character’s skin color. There are foxes, chickens, cows, and a new animal: a rhino. Notice! You only have one chance, if you are killed then you will fail! To succeed, you need to observe and react quickly. If you want a better gaming experience, you can go to the original website to experience the full-screen mode. what are you waiting for? Come and play with your friends!
By mouse and keyboard
